      <abstract id="aspace_1fff65c2531a09e8f5f9678bf0b4d666">Charles Kilgo Bradsher was a Class of
        1933 Duke alum and a Duke professor in the Chemistry Department from 1939-1979. His
        collection includes personal and departmental materials, especially concerning the Chemistry
        Department, the Gross-Edens Affair.</abstract>
